      "writtenOn": "2017-07-24T23:12:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah, ok. Yeah, if we clear data out periodically then this is ok. I would vote for a different method called GetAllRunIds() as being more obvious than relying on caller to figure out from reading docs what to pass for start/end to get them all.\n\nAnd we could move existing impl to an internal method name that both GetAllRunIds() and GetRunIDs() use.\n\nBut let\u0027s wait to hear Stephan feedback before making a change or submitting.",
      "parentUuid": "46cbe637_8a0b1b66",
      "revId": "1f4f182e952a6cfd87c82a34e18b26e73fa38d0f",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
