      "message": "To address the time issue, you could add a constant like this \n \n BeginningOfTime \u003d time.Date(2015, time.June, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, time.UTC).Unix()\n\nwhich is an arbitrary date we use in some tests. And then somebody can use:\n\n...  GetRunIDs(resultstore.BeginningOfTime, time.Now()) ...\n\nI agree that if we wanted to do pagination we should have a different interface. \nI would leave it like this for now and that can be adjusted when you query the store to present the data to the user.",
